history.content:
Weekly Event: Grad School Talk with Professors (Caltech + UCB)!  
This Monday, we will have a presentation regarding Graduate School applications, overall experience, and academic expectations with presenters from caltech and UCB!
When: Monday, 10/19, 6-7pm PST
Zoom Link https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/96692538990

Resume Drop
Part of what WiM does is help you succeed professionally! As such, we are creating a resume book that we will be sending out to companies who are looking for Math Students to work for them! Please send us your resume using the form below! 
More so, students who submit a resume will be entered into a raffle to win a prize! Be sure to send yours in!
Upload Resume: https://forms.gle/1cR2u7QZTMNeyspj9

Study Groups
Study groups have been made! Please check to see that you have been added to a slack channel for wim! If you haven't, please let me know and I can add you to one for your classes!

Website: https://wim.berkeley.edu/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/WIMatUCB/
Email: ucbwim@gmail.com let us know if you want to be on our mailing list!
history.subject: WIM Weekly update - Graduate School, Resumes, Study groups, and more!
